 and multiple nations revealing Shaligram practitioners as a distinct, alternative, community struggling for a place in a world on the edge.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aBuddhist pilgrims and pilgrimageszNepalzMustang (District). 0aHindu pilgrims and pilgrimageszNepalzMustang (District). 0aRocksxReligious aspectsxBuddhism. 0aRocksxReligious aspectsxHinduism. 0aRockszHimalaya Mountains. 0aSacred stoneszNepalzMustang (District). 0aŚālagrāma. 4aAnthropology. 4aArt and Material Culture. 4aAsian Studies. 4aCultural Studies. 4aReligion and Theology. 7aNATURE / Fossils.2bisacsh  aPilgrimage, Hinduism, Nepal, Himalayas, Fossil.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311068955608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2020 Englishz978311070480808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2020z9783110704600oZDB-23-DPM08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP ROW Ebook Package English 2020z978311069630140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048550142zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048550142423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048550142/original  a978-3-11-068955-6  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  a978-3-11-069630-1  PP ROW Ebook Package English 2020b2020  a97